OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy for most with some patchy light
OL,7,Fdrizzle at times. Staying dry in the
OL,8,Fsouthwest with some evening sunshine,
OL,9,Fthen clear spells overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,12,Fwith a little drizzle across the
OL,13,FSouthern Uplands. Dry in the afternoon
OL,14,Fwith a few sunny spells breaking
OL,15,Fthrough, mainly in the southwest.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,18,Fto Wednesday will be dry, sunny and
OL,19,Fvery warm in the west. Dry and cooler
OL,20,Fin the east, cloudier at times but
OL,21,Fstill plenty of sunny spells by day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
